NOTE: Do not access this namespace directly. Use the "sherpa.array.*" pattern instead.</description><name>sherpaArray</name><script><![CDATA[var sherpaArray = {
	/**
	* Returns true if an exact match (===) for element is found in array
	*
	* @param {Iterable} array - The array to search for element within
	* @param {Any} element - The value to search for within array
	* @return {Boolean}
	*/
	contains: function(array, element) {
		return ArrayUtil.prototype.contains(array, element);
	}
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>christopher.crockett@cloudgoservices.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-08-31 16:08:01</sys_created_on><sys_id>179202351bd27050046bca22604bcb37</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>sherpaArray</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Sherpa Utils" source="fe1202351bd27050046bca22604bcb2f">fe1202351bd27050046bca22604bcb2f</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Sherpa Utils">fe1202351bd27050046bca22604bcb2f</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_179202351bd27050046bca22604bcb37</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>christopher.crockett@cloudgoservices.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-08-31 16:10:03</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
